    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It's not really about finding comfort in the moment, though. It feels like I'm just taking up space. My kids are busy with their own lives, and I'm just... stuck in this loop of pain and loneliness. It feels like it's all just a burden now. Does that make sense?",
